/i>, which were common in the Middle Ages and gave rise to surnames, are extinct.  See also  Rupert ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Robert Gurdon was born in 1157, in Aberdeenshire, Scotland, United Kingdom. He had at least 1 son with Rose Alice Sexton. He died in 1240, in his hometown, at the age of 83, and was buried in Rhynie, Aberdeenshire, Scotland, United Kingdom."},"et":{"1157–1240":"1157–1240","1161–1220":"1161–1220","1194–1251":"1194–1251","1157":"1157","1220":"1220","1240":"1240","1251":"1251","1194":"1194","1161":"1161","Aberdeenshire, Scotland":"Aberdeenshire, Šotimaa, United Kingdom","Scudarque, Aberdeenshire, Scotland":"Aberdeenshire, Šotimaa, United Kingdom","Rhynie, Aberdeenshire, Scotland Rhynie Churchyard":"Rhynie, Aberdeenshire, Šotimaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1157–1240":"1157–1240","1161–1220":"1161–1220","1194–1251":"1194–1251","1157":"1157","1220":"1220","1240":"1240","1251":"1251","1194":"1194","1161":"1161","Aberdeenshire, Scotland":"Aberdeenshire, Skotlanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Scudarque, Aberdeenshire, Scotland":"Aberdeenshire, Skotlanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Rhynie, Aberdeenshire, Scotland Rhynie Churchyard":"Rhynie, Aberdeenshire, Skotlanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1157–1240":"1157–1240","1161–1220":"1161–1220","1194–1251":"1194–1251","1157":"1157","1220":"1220","1240":"1240","1251":"1251","1194":"1194","1161":"1161","Aberdeenshire, Scotland":"Aberdeenshire, Écosse, Royaume-Uni","Scudarque, Aberdeenshire, Scotland":"Aberdeenshire, Écosse, Royaume-Uni","Rhynie, Aberdeenshire, Scotland Rhynie Churchyard":"Rhynie, Aberdeenshire, Écosse, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Robert Gurdon est né en 1157, à Aberdeenshire, Écosse, Royaume-Uni. Il a eu au moins 1 fils avec Rose Alice Sexton. Il est décédé en 1240, dans sa ville natale, à l’âge de 83 ans, et a été enterré à Rhynie, Aberdeenshire, Écosse, Royaume-Uni."},"de":{"1157–1240":"1157–1240","1161–1220":"1161–1220","1194–1251":"1194–1251","1157":"1157","1220":"1220","1240"